reviewText:
MONDO CANE:2 IS A GREAT SHOCKUMENTEARY RIGHT DOWN TO IT'S
LAST FRONTAL LOBATOMY!!!
as good as the first one if you seen the first one you will enjoy this also. the music was not as good as the first mondo cane. Its something that there all these strange things still in this world..

Me es muy grato poder comprar y ver peliculas que no estan disponibles de otra manera, son parte de mi infancia y hace ya mas de 30 aos que las vi por primera vez.
Espero poder seguir encontrando peliculas de arte y cultura como estas.
Gracias

And in my opinion, the best of the series~
Horrific in theory rather than imagery.. Shocking in it's comparitive composition.. rather than blunt spearheaded direction.
A small price to pay for such a memorable and replayable film.
